  <brief_title>Non-invasive Assessment of Immediate Postoperative Analgesia Using Analgesia/Nociception Index (ANI)</brief_title>
  <official_title>Non-invasive Assessment of Immediate Postoperative Analgesia Using Analgesia/Nociception Index (ANI): A Prospective and Observational Study</official_title>
  <sponsors>
